hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I've only just arrived is neogyn over the counter Why is the USA doing spending our tax money on Israeli foreign policy? What are we doing employing Israelis in *our* State Department? Federal employees should be required to renounce foreign citizenship to both the US and the foreign government involved and to swear an oath renouncing allegiance to foreign States. If they want to be dual citizens and to lobby the American people for support for their pet foreign causes, fine. But not funded by reductions in food and medical care to US citizens!
